data.description: What a great home that needs a little TLC to come back to life!  Check out this 4 bedroom 2 bath home in University Park.  Please use caution when entering the property.  This home has great bones and needs some work.  The basement has had water damage and needs work.  There is potential of the basement to have additional bedrooms, a full bath and other entertaining space as well. This property is a short sale and will be sold AS-IS.  Schedule your showing today.
